name: Swimming Fish (TommiGreenBay)
description:
You are a Fish that needs to navigate through different levels.
But be careful! There are 7 different unique Enemies you should avoid.
There are also music levels, in which the level and its enemies are based on the music, but because of Copyright i had to mute some of them... I will be building new ones.
Procedural Endless and Coin Hunt Mode with High scores.
Android & PC Version. (For Android press the mobile Button in Menu)
